{"lemma":"صاغَة","slug":"صاغَة","root":"ص.#.غ","root_slug":"ص-_-غ","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-_-غ","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n25202"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D8%A7%D8%BA%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"goldsmith; jeweler"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"active participle of صَاغَ (ṣāḡa, “to shape; to mold”)."},"ipa":["/sˤaː.ʔiɣ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n25202","headword_ar":"صَاغَهُ","root":"Swg","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, MA, O, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaSuwgu","text_ar":"يَصُوغُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SawogN","text_ar":"صَوْغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, MA, O, Msb) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuwaAgN","text_ar":"صُوَاغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SiyaAgapN","text_ar":"صِيَاغَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (MA,) [or the last is a simple subst.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He melted it, and poured it forth into a mould;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he cast it, molten, in a mould:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(PS:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he made, formed, fashioned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"moulded, it, by the goldsmith's art;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, an ornament [and the like]: (MA: [this last is the most usual meaning:]) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he prepared it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cast it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) namely, a thing,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after the pattern of a right model."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) One says of a man,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAga","text_ar":"صَاغَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al*~ahaba Huliy~FA","text_ar":"الذَّهَبَ حُلِيًّا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cast the gold so as to make of it ornaments;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he made, formed, fashioned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"moulded, the gold into ornaments"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAgahu A@ll~`hu SiygapF HasanapF","text_ar":"صَاغَهُ ا@للّٰهُ صِيغَةً حَسَنَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God created him"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a goodly mode,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner, of creation."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Siyga EalaY Siygatihi","text_ar":"صِيغَ عَلَى صِيغَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1747},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was created after his"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. another's]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mode,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner, of creation."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SAg","text_ar":"صاغ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kalaAmFA","text_ar":"كَلَامًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He composed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adjusted, poetry,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"speech, discourse,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"language."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaSuwguwna AlkalaAma","text_ar":"يَصُوغُونَ الكَلَامَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They alter speech,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"embellish it with lies,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"falsify it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"forge it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN yaSuwgu Alka*iba","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ يَصُوغُ الكَذِبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S O, Msb, * TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SawogN","text_ar":"صَوْغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one forges,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fabricates, that which is false,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"untrue:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, Msb: *) a metaphorical phrase. (S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SAg fulaAnN zuwrFA","text_ar":"صاغ فُلَانٌ زُورًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ka*ibFA","text_ar":"كَذِبًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one forged,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fabricated, a lie, a falsehood,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an untruth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sawogu All~isaAni","text_ar":"صَوْغُ اللِّسَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The lying of the tongue."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 605.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SAg","text_ar":"صاغ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaSuwgu","text_ar":"يَصُوغُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SawogN","text_ar":"صَوْغٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O,) also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It sank"},{"kind":"text","text":"into the ground, said of water; and into the food, said of sauce, or seasoning: (O, K:) so says ISh. (TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SAg","text_ar":"صاغ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu Al$~araAbu","text_ar":"لَهُ الشَّرَابُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The beverage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wine, was easy and agreeable to him to swallow; i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sAg","text_ar":"ساغ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Ibn- ' Abbád, O, K,) as a dial. var. (Ibn-' Abbád, O.)"}],"source_refs":["S","MA","O","Msb","K","TA","PS"]}]}}